381
00:22:12,195 --> 00:22:15,495
If I remember correctly the letters found on the hand mirror were...

382
00:22:15,495 --> 00:22:17,595
PTON.

383
00:22:20,395 --> 00:22:23,095
The letters that were originally written on the hand mirror were...

384
00:22:23,095 --> 00:22:25,695
"Put on mascara".

385
00:22:25,695 --> 00:22:29,095
If you exclude the letters PTON,

386
00:22:29,095 --> 00:22:30,695
the remaining letters would be

387
00:22:30,695 --> 00:22:36,595
UMASCARA.

388
00:22:36,595 --> 00:22:38,495
There sure a lot of As.

389
00:22:38,495 --> 00:22:40,795
Could it be the name of a Japanese person?

390
00:22:40,795 --> 00:22:44,495
If "CA" can also be read "KA",

391
00:22:44,495 --> 00:22:45,695
then the thing that comes to mind is...

392
00:22:49,195 --> 00:22:50,795
Asaka.

393
00:22:50,795 --> 00:22:53,395
The suspect Asaka?

394
00:22:53,395 --> 00:22:58,395
If you exclude the letters ASACA from UMASCARA,

395
00:22:58,395 --> 00:23:01,095
the remainder would be UMR.

396
00:23:01,095 --> 00:23:02,495
Then if you rearrange them...

397
00:23:43,695 --> 00:23:44,995
Rum.

398
00:23:54,395 --> 00:23:57,395
"Next Episode" -Spirit Detective, Gaito Hotta?

399
