You're going to disclose the truth about the Koji Haneda murder case?

401
00:24:03,495 --> 00:24:05,495
Someone just ran from the balcony.

402
00:24:06,595 --> 00:24:07,995
Haneda...

403
00:24:07,995 --> 00:24:09,295
Koji.

